Author: myEDNOSaccount
Text: I did that for a while and it only made people concerned about me and trying to control my eating which made my ED worse. I don't talk about it IRL anymore.

Author: Iscariiot
Text: Yep. And I’d love nothing more than to be able to say when someone asks what’s wrong-  “I haven’t eaten a decent meal in weeks without vomiting it up after.”
